  **🎯 ACHIEVEMENT:**
  ✓ Target: Reduce to Rp 8M → **EXCEEDED!**
  ✓ Actual: **Rp 5M/month** (even better!)
  ✓ **Annual Savings: Rp 84,859,656** (~Rp 85M/year!)
  
  ---
  
  **📊 Cost Breakdown (New Architecture):**
  • Application VM: Rp 1,200,000 (24%)
  • hclab-server: Rp 2,040,894 (41%)
  • Load Balancer: Rp 600,000 (12%)
  • Cloud SQL: Rp 636,368 (13%)
  • Storage + Other: Rp 530,000 (10%)
  
