  **✅ Objectives Achieved:**
  1. ✓ Cost: Rp 12M → Rp 5M (Target was Rp 8M!)
  2. ✓ Region: Singapore → Jakarta
  3. ✓ Free Google-managed SSL (save Rp 1M)
  4. ✓ hclab-server untouched
  5. ✓ Simpler architecture (VM vs GKE)
  6. ✓ Better for 25-40 users scale
